  m_text: "Welcome to the Strong Man Trials!\nEncourageMan, the world\u2019s most
    motivational superhero, is about to face impossible challenges. But there\u2019s
    one secret nobody knows\u2026\n\nHis invincibility only works when someone cheers
    for him.\n\nYour job is to type hype words, fill the Hype Meter, and help EncourageMan
    survive crushing machines, deadly traps, and impossible tests of strength.\n\nIf
    your support is strong, he becomes unstoppable.\nIf your support fades\u2026
    so does he."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
